alerts.description:
There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 75-85 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 95 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: 50-60 km/h; Wind direction: west; Increased gusts: near showers and in exposed locations < 75 km/h
